#: src/introduction.md:1
msgid "Adora"
msgstr "Adora"

#: src/introduction.md:3
msgid ""
"**Agentic Dataflow-Oriented Robotic Architecture** -- a 100% Rust framework "
"for building real-time robotics and AI applications."
msgstr ""
"**智能数据流导向机器人架构** (Agentic Dataflow-Oriented Robotic Architecture) -- 一个 100% "
"Rust 的实时机器人与 AI 应用框架。"

#: src/introduction.md:5
msgid "Why Adora?"
msgstr "为什么选择 Adora？"

#: src/introduction.md:7
msgid ""
"**10-17x faster than ROS2 Python** -- zero-copy shared memory IPC, flat "
"latency from 4KB to 4MB payloads"
msgstr "**比 ROS2 Python 快 10-17 倍** -- 零拷贝共享内存 IPC，4KB 到 4MB 载荷延迟平坦"

#: src/introduction.md:8
msgid ""
"**Apache Arrow native** -- columnar memory format end-to-end with zero "
"serialization overhead"
msgstr "**Apache Arrow 原生** -- 端到端列式内存格式，零序列化开销"

#: src/introduction.md:9
msgid ""
"**Single CLI, full lifecycle** -- `adora run` for local dev, `adora up/"
"start` for distributed prod, plus build, logs, monitoring, record/replay"
msgstr "**单一 CLI，全生命周期** -- `adora run` 本地开发，`adora up/start` 分布式生产，加上构建、日志、监控、录制/回放"

#: src/introduction.md:10
msgid ""
"**Declarative YAML dataflows** -- define pipelines as directed graphs, "
"connect nodes through typed inputs/outputs"
msgstr "**声明式 YAML 数据流** -- 以有向图定义流水线，通过类型化输入/输出连接节点"

#: src/introduction.md:11
msgid ""
"**Multi-language nodes** -- write nodes in Rust, Python, C, or C++ with "
"native APIs; mix languages freely"
msgstr "**多语言节点** -- 用 Rust、Python、C 或 C++ 的原生 API 编写节点；可自由混合语言"

#: src/introduction.md:12
msgid ""
"**Fault tolerance** -- per-node restart policies, exponential backoff, "
"health monitoring, circuit breakers"
msgstr "**容错机制** -- 每节点重启策略、指数退避、健康监测、熔断器"

#: src/introduction.md:13
msgid ""
"**Distributed by default** -- local shared memory between co-located nodes, "
"automatic Zenoh pub-sub across machines"
msgstr "**天然分布式** -- 同机节点间共享内存，跨机自动 Zenoh 发布/订阅"

#: src/introduction.md:14
msgid ""
"**Record/replay** -- capture dataflow messages to `.adorec` files, replay "
"offline at any speed"
msgstr "**录制/回放** -- 将数据流消息捕获到 `.adorec` 文件，可以任意速度离线回放"

#: src/introduction.md:15
msgid ""
"**Built-in observability** -- `adora top` TUI, topic inspection, trace "
"viewing, structured logging with rotation"
msgstr "**内置可观测性** -- `adora top` TUI 监控、主题检查、追踪查看、结构化日志轮转"

