#: src/languages/c.md:28
msgid "Node API (adora-node-api-c)"
msgstr "节点 API (adora-node-api-c)"

#: src/languages/c.md:30
msgid ""
"Header: [`apis/c/node/node_api.h`](../apis/c/node/node_api.h) Crate: `adora-"
"node-api-c` (builds as `staticlib`)"
msgstr ""
"头文件：[`apis/c/node/node_api.h`](../apis/c/node/node_api.h) "
"Crate：`adora-node-api-c`（构建为 `staticlib`）"

#: src/languages/c.md:33
msgid ""
"The Node API is used by standalone C executables that participate in an "
"Adora dataflow as external processes. The daemon spawns the process and sets "
"environment variables that the node reads during initialization."
msgstr "节点 API 供作为外部进程参与 Adora 数据流的独立 C 可执行文件使用。守护进程生成进程并设置节点在初始化期间读取的环境变量。"

#: src/languages/c.md:37
msgid "`init_adora_context_from_env`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:43
msgid ""
"Initializes an Adora node context from environment variables set by the "
"daemon. Returns an opaque pointer to the context on success, or `NULL` on "
"failure."
msgstr "从守护进程设置的环境变量初始化 Adora 节点上下文。成功时返回指向上下文的不透明指针，失败时返回 `NULL`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:45
msgid ""
"The returned pointer must be passed to all subsequent Node API calls that "
"expect a context argument. When the node is finished, free it with "
"`free_adora_context`."
msgstr "返回的指针必须传递给所有期望上下文参数的后续节点 API 调用。节点完成后，使用 `free_adora_context` 释放。"

#: src/languages/c.md:47
msgid "`free_adora_context`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:53
msgid ""
"Frees a context previously created by `init_adora_context_from_env`. Each "
"context must be freed exactly once. After freeing, the pointer must not be "
"used again."
msgstr "释放先前由 `init_adora_context_from_env` 创建的上下文。每个上下文必须恰好释放一次。释放后不得再次使用该指针。"

#: src/languages/c.md:55
msgid "Event Loop"
msgstr "事件循环"

#: src/languages/c.md:57
msgid "`adora_next_event`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:63
msgid ""
"Blocks until the next event is available for this node. Returns an opaque "
"pointer to the event, or `NULL` when all event streams have closed "
"(indicating the node should exit)."
msgstr "阻塞直到此节点有可用的下一个事件。返回指向事件的不透明指针，当所有事件流关闭时返回 `NULL`（表示节点应退出）。"

#: src/languages/c.md:65
msgid ""
"The returned pointer must not be dereferenced directly. Use the "
"`read_adora_*` functions to extract the event type and payload. Free the "
"event with `free_adora_event` when done."
msgstr "返回的指针不能直接解引用。使用 `read_adora_*` 函数提取事件类型和载荷。完成后使用 `free_adora_event` 释放事件。"

#: src/languages/c.md:67
msgid "`free_adora_event`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:73
msgid ""
"Frees an event previously returned by `adora_next_event`. Each event must be "
"freed exactly once. After freeing, the event pointer and all derived "
"pointers (from `read_adora_input_id`, `read_adora_input_data`) become "
"invalid."
msgstr ""
"释放先前由 `adora_next_event` 返回的事件。每个事件必须恰好释放一次。释放后，事件指针和所有派生指针（来自 "
"`read_adora_input_id`、`read_adora_input_data`）都将失效。"

#: src/languages/c.md:75
msgid "Event Inspection"
msgstr "事件检查"

#: src/languages/c.md:77
msgid "`read_adora_event_type`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:83
msgid ""
"Returns the type of the given event. See [AdoraEventType](#adoraeventtype) "
"for possible values."
msgstr "返回给定事件的类型。可能的值请参见 [AdoraEventType](#adoraeventtype)。"

#: src/languages/c.md:85
msgid "`read_adora_input_id`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:91
msgid ""
"Reads the input ID from an `AdoraEventType_Input` event. Writes the string "
"start pointer to `*out_ptr` and its byte length to `*out_len`. The string is "
"valid UTF-8 but **not** null-terminated; use `out_len` to determine its "
"bounds."
msgstr ""
"从 `AdoraEventType_Input` 事件读取输入 ID。将字符串起始指针写入 `*out_ptr`，字节长度写入 "
"`*out_len`。字符串是有效的 UTF-8 但**不**以 null 结尾；使用 `out_len` 确定其边界。"

#: src/languages/c.md:93
msgid ""
"If the event is not an input event, sets `*out_ptr = NULL` and `*out_len = "
"0`."
msgstr "如果事件不是输入事件，则设置 `*out_ptr = NULL` 和 `*out_len = 0`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:95 src/languages/c.md:109
msgid ""
"The returned pointer borrows from the event. It becomes invalid after "
"`free_adora_event` is called."
msgstr "返回的指针借用自事件。调用 `free_adora_event` 后将失效。"

#: src/languages/c.md:97
msgid "`read_adora_input_data`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:103
msgid ""
"Reads the raw data bytes from an `AdoraEventType_Input` event. Writes the "
"data start pointer to `*out_ptr` and its byte length to `*out_len`."
msgstr "从 `AdoraEventType_Input` 事件读取原始数据字节。将数据起始指针写入 `*out_ptr`，字节长度写入 `*out_len`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:105
msgid ""
"Sets `*out_ptr = NULL` and `*out_len = 0` if the event is not an input event "
"or the input carries no data."
msgstr "如果事件不是输入事件或输入不携带数据，则设置 `*out_ptr = NULL` 和 `*out_len = 0`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:107
msgid ""
"Currently only `UInt8` Arrow arrays are supported. Other Arrow data types "
"will cause a runtime panic. Future versions will use the Arrow C Data "
"Interface for full type support."
msgstr ""
"目前仅支持 `UInt8` Arrow 数组。其他 Arrow 数据类型会导致运行时 panic。未来版本将使用 Arrow C Data "
"Interface 以支持所有类型。"

#: src/languages/c.md:111
msgid "`read_adora_input_timestamp`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:117
msgid ""
"Returns the hybrid logical clock timestamp from an input event's metadata as "
"a `uint64` value. Returns `0` if the event is not an input event."
msgstr "以 `uint64` 值形式返回输入事件元数据中的混合逻辑时钟时间戳。如果事件不是输入事件则返回 `0`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:119
msgid "Output"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:121
msgid "`adora_send_output`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:133
msgid ""
"Sends output data to all downstream subscribers. The output ID (`id_ptr`/"
"`id_len`) must be a valid UTF-8 string matching one of the node's declared "
"outputs in the dataflow YAML. The data (`data_ptr`/`data_len`) is sent as "
"raw bytes (UInt8 Arrow array)."
msgstr ""
"向所有下游订阅者发送输出数据。输出 ID（`id_ptr`/`id_len`）必须是有效的 UTF-8 字符串，与数据流 YAML "
"中节点声明的某个输出匹配。数据（`data_ptr`/`data_len`）作为原始字节（UInt8 Arrow 数组）发送。"

#: src/languages/c.md:135
msgid "Returns `0` on success, `-1` on error. Errors are logged via `tracing`."
msgstr "成功返回 `0`，错误返回 `-1`。错误通过 `tracing` 记录。"

#: src/languages/c.md:137
msgid "Returns `-1` immediately if any pointer argument is `NULL`."
msgstr "如果任何指针参数为 `NULL`，则立即返回 `-1`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:141
msgid "`adora_log`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:153
msgid ""
"Sends a structured log message through the Adora logging pipeline. Both "
"`level` and `msg` must be valid UTF-8 strings."
msgstr "通过 Adora 日志管道发送结构化日志消息。`level` 和 `msg` 都必须是有效的 UTF-8 字符串。"

#: src/languages/c.md:155
msgid ""
"Valid log levels: `\"error\"`, `\"warn\"`, `\"info\"`, `\"debug\"`, "
"`\"trace\"`."
msgstr "有效的日志级别：`\"error\"`、`\"warn\"`、`\"info\"`、`\"debug\"`、`\"trace\"`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:157
msgid ""
"Returns `0` on success, `-1` on error. Returns `-1` immediately if any "
"pointer argument is `NULL`."
msgstr "成功返回 `0`，错误返回 `-1`。如果任何指针参数为 `NULL`，则立即返回 `-1`。"

