#: src/languages/c.md:175
msgid "Operator API (adora-operator-api-c)"
msgstr "算子 API (adora-operator-api-c)"

#: src/languages/c.md:177
msgid ""
"Headers: [`apis/c/operator/operator_api.h`](../apis/c/operator/"
"operator_api.h), [`apis/c/operator/operator_types.h`](../apis/c/operator/"
"operator_types.h) Crate: `adora-operator-api-c`"
msgstr ""
"头文件：[`apis/c/operator/operator_api.h`](../apis/c/operator/operator_api.h)、[`apis/c/operator/operator_types.h`](../apis/c/operator/operator_types.h) "
"Crate：`adora-operator-api-c`"

#: src/languages/c.md:180
msgid ""
"The Operator API is used by shared libraries (`.so`/`.dylib`/`.dll`) loaded "
"into the Adora runtime process. Unlike nodes, operators do not have their "
"own `main` function. Instead, they export three functions that the runtime "
"calls at the appropriate lifecycle points."
msgstr ""
"算子 API 供加载到 Adora 运行时进程中的共享库（`.so`/`.dylib`/`.dll`）使用。与节点不同，算子没有自己的 `main` "
"函数。它们导出三个函数，由运行时在适当的生命周期点调用。"

#: src/languages/c.md:182
msgid ""
"The `operator_types.h` header is auto-generated by `safer-ffi` and defines "
"all C-compatible struct and enum types."
msgstr "`operator_types.h` 头文件由 `safer-ffi` 自动生成，定义了所有 C 兼容的结构体和枚举类型。"

#: src/languages/c.md:184
msgid "Lifecycle Functions"
msgstr "生命周期函数"

#: src/languages/c.md:186
msgid "`adora_init_operator`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:192
msgid ""
"Called once when the runtime loads the operator. Allocate and initialize any "
"operator state, then return it via the `operator_context` field. The runtime "
"passes this pointer back on every subsequent call."
msgstr "运行时加载算子时调用一次。分配并初始化所有算子状态，然后通过 `operator_context` 字段返回。运行时在每次后续调用中传回此指针。"

#: src/languages/c.md:194
msgid "Return an `AdoraInitResult_t` with `.result.error = NULL` on success."
msgstr "成功时返回 `.result.error = NULL` 的 `AdoraInitResult_t`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:196
msgid "`adora_drop_operator`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:202
msgid ""
"Called once when the operator is being unloaded. Free all resources "
"associated with `operator_context`."
msgstr "算子被卸载时调用一次。释放与 `operator_context` 关联的所有资源。"

#: src/languages/c.md:204
msgid "Return an `AdoraResult_t` with `.error = NULL` on success."
msgstr "成功时返回 `.error = NULL` 的 `AdoraResult_t`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:206
msgid "Event Handling"
msgstr "事件处理"

#: src/languages/c.md:208
msgid "`adora_on_event`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:218
msgid ""
"Called by the runtime each time an event arrives for this operator. Inspect "
"the `event` fields to determine the event type:"
msgstr "每当此算子有事件到达时由运行时调用。检查 `event` 字段以确定事件类型："

#: src/languages/c.md:220 src/operations/logging.md:47
#: src/operations/distributed.md:141 src/operations/distributed.md:148
#: src/operations/distributed.md:813 src/advanced/ros2-bridge.md:404
#: src/advanced/ros2-bridge.md:438 src/advanced/ws-control.md:64
#: src/advanced/ws-control.md:88 src/advanced/ws-topic.md:106
msgid "Field"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:222
msgid "`event->input != NULL`"
msgstr "`event->input != NULL`"

#: src/languages/c.md:222
msgid "New input available"
msgstr "有新输入可用"

#: src/languages/c.md:223
msgid "`event->stop == true`"
msgstr "`event->stop == true`"

#: src/languages/c.md:223
msgid "Graceful shutdown requested"
msgstr "请求优雅关闭"

#: src/languages/c.md:224
msgid "`event->error.ptr != NULL`"
msgstr "`event->error.ptr != NULL`"

#: src/languages/c.md:224
msgid "An error occurred (UTF-8 string in `error.ptr`/`error.len`)"
msgstr "发生错误（UTF-8 字符串位于 `error.ptr`/`error.len`）"

#: src/languages/c.md:225
msgid "`event->input_closed.ptr != NULL`"
msgstr "`event->input_closed.ptr != NULL`"

#: src/languages/c.md:225
msgid ""
"An input stream closed (input ID in `input_closed.ptr`/`input_closed.len`)"
msgstr "输入流已关闭（输入 ID 位于 `input_closed.ptr`/`input_closed.len`）"

#: src/languages/c.md:227
msgid ""
"Use `send_output` to emit data to downstream nodes (see "
"`adora_send_operator_output`). Return an `OnEventResult_t` with the "
"appropriate `AdoraStatus_t` to control the operator lifecycle."
msgstr ""
"使用 `send_output` 向下游节点发送数据（见 `adora_send_operator_output`）。返回带有适当 "
"`AdoraStatus_t` 的 `OnEventResult_t` 以控制算子生命周期。"

#: src/languages/c.md:229
msgid "Input Reading"
msgstr "输入读取"

#: src/languages/c.md:231 src/languages/c.md:272
msgid "`adora_read_input_id`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:237
msgid ""
"Returns a newly allocated null-terminated string containing the input ID. "
"The caller must free it with `adora_free_input_id`."
msgstr "返回新分配的以 null 结尾的字符串，包含输入 ID。调用者必须使用 `adora_free_input_id` 释放。"

#: src/languages/c.md:239 src/languages/c.md:273
msgid "`adora_read_data`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:245
msgid ""
"Reads the input data as a byte array. Consumes the underlying Arrow array "
"from the input (the data can only be read once per event). Returns a "
"`Vec_uint8_t` with `.ptr = NULL` if the input has no data or the data has "
"already been consumed."
msgstr ""
"将输入数据作为字节数组读取。从输入中消费底层 Arrow 数组（每个事件只能读取一次数据）。如果输入没有数据或数据已被消费，则返回 `.ptr = "
"NULL` 的 `Vec_uint8_t`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:247
msgid "The caller must free the returned data with `adora_free_data`."
msgstr "调用者必须使用 `adora_free_data` 释放返回的数据。"

#: src/languages/c.md:249
msgid "Output Sending"
msgstr "输出发送"

#: src/languages/c.md:251
msgid "`adora_send_operator_output`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:262
msgid ""
"Sends output data to downstream subscribers. The `id` must be a null-"
"terminated string matching one of the operator's declared outputs. The data "
"(`data_ptr`/`data_len`) is converted to a UInt8 Arrow array internally."
msgstr ""
"向下游订阅者发送输出数据。`id` 必须是以 null "
"结尾的字符串，与算子声明的某个输出匹配。数据（`data_ptr`/`data_len`）在内部被转换为 UInt8 Arrow 数组。"

#: src/languages/c.md:264
msgid "Returns an `AdoraResult_t` with `.error = NULL` on success."
msgstr "成功时返回 `.error = NULL` 的 `AdoraResult_t`。"

#: src/languages/c.md:266
msgid "Memory Management"
msgstr "内存管理"

#: src/languages/c.md:268
msgid ""
"The Operator API allocates memory that the caller must free using the "
"corresponding functions:"
msgstr "算子 API 分配的内存必须由调用者使用相应的函数释放："

#: src/languages/c.md:270
msgid "Allocation source"
msgstr "分配来源"

#: src/languages/c.md:270
msgid "Free function"
msgstr "释放函数"

#: src/languages/c.md:272
msgid "`adora_free_input_id`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:273
msgid "`adora_free_data`"
msgstr ""

#: src/languages/c.md:280
msgid ""
"Failing to call these functions will leak memory. Do not use `free()` on "
"these allocations -- they are allocated by the Rust runtime and must be "
"freed through the API."
