#: src/operations/logging.md:228
msgid ""
"When `--since`, `--until`, or `--grep` are used in coordinator mode, the CLI "
"fetches all logs from the server (ignoring `--tail` server-side) and applies "
"all filters client-side. This ensures correct results when combining filters."
msgstr ""
"在协调器模式下使用 `--since`、`--until` 或 `--grep` 时，CLI 从服务器获取所有日志（忽略服务端的 "
"`--tail`）并在客户端应用所有过滤器。这确保了组合使用过滤器时结果的正确性。"

#: src/operations/logging.md:230
msgid "Local vs Coordinator Mode"
msgstr "本地模式 vs 协调器模式"

#: src/operations/logging.md:232
msgid ""
"**Local mode** (`--local`) reads JSONL files directly from the `out/` "
"directory in the current working directory. No coordinator or daemon needs "
"to be running. If `--all-nodes` is used or no node name is given, all log "
"files are merged and sorted by timestamp."
msgstr ""
"**本地模式**（`--local`）直接从当前工作目录的 `out/` 目录读取 JSONL 文件。无需运行协调器或守护进程。如果使用 "
"`--all-nodes` 或未指定节点名称，所有日志文件将合并并按时间戳排序。"

#: src/operations/logging.md:234
msgid ""
"**Coordinator mode** (default) connects to a running coordinator via "
"WebSocket. The coordinator reads log files from the daemon's working "
"directory and streams them back. This works for both local and distributed "
"deployments."
msgstr "**协调器模式**（默认）通过 WebSocket 连接到运行中的协调器。协调器从守护进程的工作目录读取日志文件并将其回传。适用于本地和分布式部署。"

#: src/operations/logging.md:236
msgid "Follow Mode"
msgstr "跟踪模式"

#: src/operations/logging.md:238
msgid ""
"**Local follow** (`--local --follow`): Polls log files every 200ms for new "
"content. New lines are parsed, filtered by `--grep`, and printed. Time/tail "
"filters only apply to the initial historical output."
msgstr ""
"**本地跟踪**（`--local --follow`）：每 200ms 轮询日志文件获取新内容。新行被解析、经 `--grep` "
"过滤后打印。时间/尾部过滤器仅应用于初始历史输出。"

#: src/operations/logging.md:240
msgid ""
"**Coordinator follow** (`--follow`): Opens a WebSocket subscription to the "
"coordinator. The coordinator forwards log messages from the daemon in real-"
"time. Level filtering is applied server-side for efficiency. `--grep` and `--"
"since` are applied client-side on the stream."
msgstr ""
"**协调器跟踪**（`--follow`）：向协调器打开 WebSocket "
"订阅。协调器实时转发守护进程的日志消息。级别过滤在服务端应用以提高效率。`--grep` 和 `--since` 在客户端对流应用。"

#: src/operations/logging.md:246
msgid ""
"All environment variables serve as fallbacks -- CLI flags always take "
"precedence."
msgstr "所有环境变量作为备选值 -- CLI 标志始终优先。"

