#: src/operations/logging.md:796
msgid ""
"**sensor** -- Mixes `print()` (raw stdout), `logging.info()`, "
"`logging.debug()`, and `logging.warning()`. With `min_log_level: info`, "
"debug messages are dropped by the daemon before reaching log files. With "
"`max_log_size: \"1KB\"`, log rotation kicks in after a few seconds."
