#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:3
msgid ""
"Adora provides built-in fault tolerance for robotic and AI dataflows. Nodes "
"can automatically restart on failure, detect stale upstream connections, "
"gracefully degrade when inputs are unavailable, and the coordinator can "
"persist state to disk so it survives crashes and restarts."
msgstr ""
"Adora 为机器人和 AI "
"数据流提供了内置的容错能力。节点可以在故障时自动重启、检测上游连接过期、在输入不可用时优雅降级，同时协调器可以将状态持久化到磁盘以便在崩溃和重启后恢复。"

