#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:417
msgid "Dataflow Status Lifecycle"
msgstr "数据流状态生命周期"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:419
msgid "The coordinator persists dataflow status at every state transition:"
msgstr "协调器在每次状态转换时持久化数据流状态："

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:421
msgid ""
"```\n"
"Start command     -->  Pending\n"
"All daemons ready -->  Running\n"
"Stop command      -->  Stopping\n"
"All nodes finish  -->  Succeeded  or  Failed { error }\n"
"Spawn failure     -->  Failed { error: \"spawn failed: ...\" }\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:429
msgid ""
"Each persist call increments the record's `generation` counter, providing a "
"monotonic version for conflict detection."
msgstr "每次持久化调用递增记录的 `generation` 计数器，提供用于冲突检测的单调版本。"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:431
msgid "Persistence Points"
msgstr "持久化点"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:433
msgid "The coordinator writes to the store at these moments in the event loop:"
msgstr "协调器在事件循环的以下时刻写入存储："

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:435
msgid ""
"**Dataflow started** (`ControlRequest::Start`) -- record created with status "
"`Pending`"
msgstr "**数据流启动** (`ControlRequest::Start`) —— 创建状态为 `Pending` 的记录"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:436
msgid ""
"**Dataflow spawned** (`DataflowSpawnResult` success from all daemons) -- "
"updated to `Running`"
msgstr "**数据流已生成** (所有守护进程的 `DataflowSpawnResult` 成功) —— 更新为 `Running`"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:437
msgid ""
"**Spawn failed** (`DataflowSpawnResult` error) -- updated to `Failed` with "
"the actual error message"
msgstr "**生成失败** (`DataflowSpawnResult` 错误) —— 更新为 `Failed` 并附带实际错误消息"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:438
msgid ""
"**Stop requested** (`ControlRequest::Stop` or `StopByName`) -- updated to "
"`Stopping`"
msgstr "**请求停止** (`ControlRequest::Stop` 或 `StopByName`) —— 更新为 `Stopping`"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:439
msgid ""
"**All nodes finished** (`DataflowFinishedOnDaemon`) -- updated to "
"`Succeeded` or `Failed` with per-node error details"
msgstr ""
"**所有节点完成** (`DataflowFinishedOnDaemon`) —— 更新为 `Succeeded` 或 `Failed` "
"并附带每个节点的错误详情"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:440
msgid ""
"**Graceful shutdown** (Ctrl-C or `Destroy` command) -- all running dataflows "
"marked `Stopping` before stop messages are sent"
msgstr "**优雅关闭**（Ctrl-C 或 `Destroy` 命令）—— 在发送停止消息之前将所有运行中的数据流标记为 `Stopping`"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:442
msgid ""
"If a store write fails, the coordinator logs a warning and continues "
"operating with in-memory state. This prevents a store failure from blocking "
"the dataflow lifecycle."
msgstr "如果存储写入失败，协调器记录警告并继续使用内存状态运行。这防止存储故障阻塞数据流生命周期。"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:444
msgid "Startup Recovery"
msgstr "启动恢复"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:446
msgid ""
"When the coordinator starts with a redb store that contains data from a "
"previous run, it performs recovery:"
msgstr "当协调器使用包含上次运行数据的 redb 存储启动时，它执行恢复："

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:448
msgid "Read all persisted dataflow records via `store.list_dataflows()`"
msgstr "通过 `store.list_dataflows()` 读取所有持久化的数据流记录"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:449
msgid ""
"For any record with a non-terminal status (`Pending`, `Running`, `Stopping`):"
msgstr "对于任何非终态状态（`Pending`、`Running`、`Stopping`）的记录："

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:450
msgid "Mark it as `Failed { error: \"coordinator restarted\" }`"
msgstr "将其标记为 `Failed { error: \"coordinator restarted\" }`"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:451
msgid "Increment the generation counter"
msgstr "递增 generation 计数器"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:452
msgid "Write the updated record back to the store"
msgstr "将更新后的记录写回存储"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:453
msgid "Terminal records (`Succeeded`, `Failed`) are left unchanged"
msgstr "终态记录（`Succeeded`、`Failed`）保持不变"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:455
msgid ""
"This ensures that stale dataflows from a crashed coordinator are not "
"confused with actively running ones. The daemons that were running those "
"dataflows will detect the coordinator disconnect independently."
msgstr "这确保了崩溃的协调器遗留的过期数据流不会与正在运行的数据流混淆。运行这些数据流的守护进程将独立检测到协调器断开。"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:457
msgid "Error Detail Preservation"
msgstr "错误详情保留"

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:459
msgid ""
"When a dataflow fails, the `Failed` status includes the actual per-node "
"error messages rather than a generic string:"
msgstr "当数据流失败时，`Failed` 状态包含实际的每节点错误消息，而非通用字符串："

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:461
msgid ""
"```\n"
"Failed { error: \"node-1: exited with code 137; node-2: failed to spawn "
"node: binary not found\" }\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/operations/fault-tolerance.md:465
