msgstr "可靠性、持久性、历史、活跃度"

#: src/advanced/ros2-bridge.md:17
msgid "Auto-spawn"
msgstr ""

#: src/advanced/ros2-bridge.md:17
msgid "Bridge binary spawned by daemon as a Custom node"
msgstr "守护进程作为自定义节点生成桥接二进制文件"

#: src/advanced/ros2-bridge.md:23
msgid ""
"When the Adora descriptor resolver encounters a `ros2:` key on a node, it "
"converts it into a `Custom` node pointing to the `adora-ros2-bridge-node` "
"binary. The bridge config is serialized as JSON into the "
"`ADORA_ROS2_BRIDGE_CONFIG` environment variable."
msgstr ""
"当 Adora 描述符解析器在节点上遇到 `ros2:` 键时，它将其转换为指向 `adora-ros2-bridge-node` 二进制文件的 "
"`Custom` 节点。桥接配置被序列化为 JSON 到 `ADORA_ROS2_BRIDGE_CONFIG` 环境变量中。"

#: src/advanced/ros2-bridge.md:29
msgid "The bridge binary:"
msgstr "桥接二进制文件："

#: src/advanced/ros2-bridge.md:31
msgid "Reads `AMENT_PREFIX_PATH` to locate installed ROS2 message packages"
msgstr "读取 `AMENT_PREFIX_PATH` 以定位已安装的 ROS2 消息包"

#: src/advanced/ros2-bridge.md:32
msgid "Parses message/service/action definitions at startup"
msgstr "启动时解析消息/服务/动作定义"

#: src/advanced/ros2-bridge.md:33
msgid ""
"Creates a `ros2_client` node and the appropriate publishers, subscribers, "
"clients, or servers"
msgstr "创建 `ros2_client` 节点和相应的发布者、订阅者、客户端或服务端"

#: src/advanced/ros2-bridge.md:34
msgid ""
"Converts incoming ROS2 CDR messages to Arrow `StructArray` (subscribe/"
"response/feedback)"
msgstr "将传入的 ROS2 CDR 消息转换为 Arrow `StructArray`（订阅/响应/反馈）"

#: src/advanced/ros2-bridge.md:35
msgid ""
"Converts incoming Arrow `StructArray` to ROS2 CDR messages (publish/request/"
"goal)"
msgstr "将传入的 Arrow `StructArray` 转换为 ROS2 CDR 消息（发布/请求/目标）"

#: src/advanced/ros2-bridge.md:37
msgid ""
"Your user nodes never link against ROS2 -- all ROS2 communication is "
"isolated in the bridge binary."
msgstr "你的用户节点永远不会链接 ROS2——所有 ROS2 通信都隔离在桥接二进制文件中。"

#: src/advanced/ros2-bridge.md:43
msgid ""
"**ROS2 environment sourced**: `AMENT_PREFIX_PATH` must be set and point to a "
"workspace containing the required message packages"
msgstr "**已 source ROS2 环境**：`AMENT_PREFIX_PATH` 必须设置并指向包含所需消息包的工作空间"

#: src/advanced/ros2-bridge.md:44
msgid ""
"**Message packages installed**: e.g., `turtlesim`, `geometry_msgs`, "
"`example_interfaces`"
msgstr "**已安装消息包**：例如 `turtlesim`、`geometry_msgs`、`example_interfaces`"

#: src/advanced/ros2-bridge.md:45
msgid ""
"**For service client**: A ROS2 service server must be running (or use a "
"companion server dataflow)"
msgstr "**服务客户端**：ROS2 服务服务端必须正在运行（或使用配套的服务端数据流）"

#: src/advanced/ros2-bridge.md:46
msgid ""
"**For action client**: A ROS2 action server must be running _before_ "
"starting the dataflow (no `wait_for_action_server` mechanism)"
msgstr "**动作客户端**：ROS2 动作服务端必须在启动数据流_之前_运行（无 `wait_for_action_server` 机制）"

#: src/advanced/ros2-bridge.md:47
msgid ""
"**For action server**: A ROS2 action client sends goals to the bridge (e.g., "
"`ros2 action send_goal`)"
msgstr "**动作服务端**：ROS2 动作客户端向桥接发送目标（例如 `ros2 action send_goal`）"

