#: src/advanced/ws-control.md:181
msgid ""
"`WsSession` is a synchronous wrapper that bridges blocking CLI code to the "
"async WebSocket connection. It creates an internal `tokio::runtime::Runtime` "
"(current-thread) and spawns an async `session_loop` task."
msgstr ""
"`WsSession` 是一个同步包装器，将阻塞的 CLI 代码桥接到异步 WebSocket 连接。它创建内部的 "
"`tokio::runtime::Runtime`（当前线程）并生成异步 `session_loop` 任务。"

